      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "parametrize_used_for_repeats": false,
  "ids_present": false,
  "no_cartesian_explosion": false,
  "pytest_param_for_per_case_marks": false
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates red; methodology not applied — fix the violations before claiming completion.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Every required field is present and boolean true.</item>
      <item>Artefact references the rule id from 01-core-rules.xml (e.g., r1-parametrize-for-repeats).</item>
      <item>No extra properties outside the schema.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
